{"tid":1942664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前兩日六十歲手足俾狗拉左，然後網上只有狗自編自演之論","createTime":"2020-03-25T08:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T08:33:23.000Z","uid":183649,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66b89ffd99599a232ecdfd48dd53db8a6d2a0680","tid":1942664,"uid":183649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2955340854526030/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F498203090239831%2Fposts%2F2955340854526030%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=3d7e7869\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2955340854526030/</a><br />\n一名退休男子前日（23日）凌晨涉在上水已婚警察宿舍擲汽油彈，今（25日）被解至西九龍裁判法院提堂，裁判官押後案件至6月底待警方調查，被告在未有保釋申請下還押候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告黃錦全（62歲）報稱已退休，暫毋須答辯。控罪指稱他於2020年3月23日在上水已婚警察宿舍外，無合法辯解而用火損壞一輛私家車。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被告當日凌晨向宿舍停車場擲4枚汽油彈，其中3支跌在停車場內，警方接報到場，在附近截查正踏單車的被告，搜查單車時發現一支懷疑易燃物品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官應控方要求，將案件押後至6月26日再訊，待警方進一步調查。由於被告沒申請保釋，須還押候訊，辯方稱會稍後申請保釋。"},{"pid":"63bf9d8bd24c57b80a1ee2e507f964e7931ffbf3","tid":1942664,"uid":183649,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"老年手足唔係手足？!<br />\n當日藏槍既又話鬼<br />\n今日掟狗屋既都係鬼<br />\n<br />\n停止捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n繼續抗爭好嗎？"},{"pid":"d1297e15818cfc73ae4907bcddaf62fbe8148f2c","tid":1942664,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef8793d6e7530ca20f8f20e8f0f2d505bfad9f2","tid":1942664,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"快啲保釋完出嚟先"},{"pid":"70533abcb125870654f44051f45535f3702167a7","tid":1942664,"uid":337826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"老手足跑得無咁快都夠膽出嚟<br />\n真係令我地呢啲鍵盤戰士無面見人"},{"pid":"7f6a39b4ad61f7f39650d8e3070e5aa28b51577a","tid":1942664,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58afad3b70cdbf1ecc08953ead99ef4a623be6e","tid":1942664,"uid":29143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"4fc610fa3f51cad84fb7f3d0c72d9b580c6e0ab8","tid":1942664,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"我諗唔到有咩藉口放棄<br />\n唔好善忘啊 香港人"},{"pid":"e98dd23a44ecd4d97b2611e9e76c2f7452c5ed90","tid":1942664,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f586cbb17020deecfe2d6597dbe5fb2b4b96c32","tid":1942664,"uid":183649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"何解血在淚  捉鬼分化聲響透？"},{"pid":"45c39f4a8143c6af15c1b674394ea1c5e2bb00fe","tid":1942664,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}